 Oasis 宣布 30 周年纪念版《Definitely Maybe》将重新发行，其中收录了前所未闻的版本https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-30th-anniversary-reissue-of-definitely-maybe-featuring-unheard-versions-3758723?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=oasis-announce-30th-周年纪念重新发行，绝对可能具有闻所未闻的版本Tom SkinnerThu, 23 May 2024 08:00:55 +0000 Music NewsNewsBritpopIndie https://www.nme.com/?p=3758723 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Oasis 的 Noel 和 Liam Gallagher 的黑白照片" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>未发行的录音和剪辑将为歌迷提供对乐队经典首张专辑的“令人着迷的新见解”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-30th-anniversary-reissue-of-definitely-maybe-featuring-unheard-versions-3758723">Oasis 宣布 30 周年纪念版《Definitely Maybe》重新发行，其中收录了前所未闻的版本，该</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Oasis 的 Noel 和 Liam Gallagher 的黑白照片" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/OasisDefinitelyMaybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>宣布将重新发行《Definitely Maybe》30 周年纪念版，收录了以前闻所未闻的录音和片段。查找下面的所有详细信息。</p><p>英国流行乐队 1994 年首张专辑的特别版将于 8 月 30 日通过 Big Brother Recordings 发行。它将以限量版 4LP 唱片、豪华 2CD、独家彩色黑胶唱片和其他格式提供 -<a href="https://oasismusic.lnk.to/DM30" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此预订</a>。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/noel-gallagher-interview-oasis-council-skies-3451058">诺埃尔·加拉格尔（Noel Gallagher）：“世界是一个美丽的地方——只是居住着混蛋”</a></strong></li></ul><p> “Definitely Maybe（30 周年豪华版）”包含来自 Monnow Valley Studios 废弃的原始录音部分的曲目，以及在康沃尔郡 Sawmills Studios 录制的片段 - 由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">Noel Gallagher</a>和 Callum Marinho 首次混音。</p><p>该专辑还包括未发行的“悲伤歌曲”演示版本。这首另类歌曲最初作为附赠曲目发行，由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔</a>(Liam Gallagher) 演唱。</p><p>此外，再版还包含由 Microdot 原创艺术设计师 Brian Cannon 和原创封面摄影师 Michael Spencer Jones 创作的全新艺术作品，以及 Creation Records 老板 Alan McGee 和记者 Hamish MacBain 的新封面笔记。</p><p>独家彩色黑胶唱片包括受“Up In The Sky”抒情启发的蓝色和白色大理石 2LP，以及受“Digsy&#39;s Dining”抒情启发的粉色和白色大理石 2LP。粉丝们还可以购买限量版蓝色磁带，并在数字平台上预购/预存。</p><p>所有格式均包含 2014 年重制版本的“Definitely Maybe”。查看下面的预览图像。 </p><figure id="attachment_3758738" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3758738" style="width: 3000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-