tps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-4-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3758739" class="wp-caption-text"> Oasis &#39;Definitely Maybe&#39; 30 周年纪念再版。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3758740" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3758740" style="width: 3000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3758740" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-5.jpg" alt="Oasis &#39;Definitely Maybe&#39; 30 周年纪念再版" width="3000" height="3000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-5.jpg 3000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-5-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-5-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-5-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-5-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-5-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-5-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3758740" class="wp-caption-text"> Oasis &#39;Definitely Maybe&#39; 30 周年纪念再版。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3758741" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3758741" style="width: 3000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3758741" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-6.jpg" alt="Oasis &#39;Definitely Maybe&#39; 30 周年纪念再版" width="3000" height="3000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-6.jpg 3000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-6-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-6-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-6-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-6-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-6-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Oasis-Definitely-Maybe-reissue-6-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3758741" class="wp-caption-text"> Oasis &#39;Definitely Maybe&#39; 30 周年纪念再版。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>描述中写道：“在签署了一份全球唱片合约后，利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher)、诺埃尔·加拉格尔 (Noel Gallagher)、保罗·‘笨头’·亚瑟斯 (Paul &#39;Bonehead&#39; Arthurs)、保罗·麦奎根 (Paul McGuigan) 和托尼·麦卡罗尔 (Tony McCarroll) 逃到蒙茅斯郡威尔士边境的蒙诺谷工作室，捕捉他们现场表演的动能。记录在案。</p><p> “当时，最初的录音感觉过于技术化和精致，未能捕捉到乐队的精髓。这些会议最终被取消，乐队搬到康沃尔郡锯木厂录音室的偏远地区重新录制专辑。最终，随着欧文·莫里斯的加入完成了最终的混音，《Definitely Maybe》就这样形成了。”</p><p>它补充道：“蒙诺谷的录音和锯木厂的录音现在首次出土，为最终完成的文章的过程提供了新的、令人信服的理解。</p><p> “凭借其原始的边缘和不安的能量，《Definitely Maybe》听起来总是像是一张已经完全成型的专辑——然而，新发布的版本为歌迷提供了对这张专辑的迷人的新见解；展示了早年推动 Oasis 发展的自信以及首次亮相所需的决心。</p><p> “直到现在，重新审视 30 年后的档案，表明了录音过程在讲述有史以来最重要的专辑之一的艰难创作故事方面的重要性。”</p><p> 《Definitely Maybe》在​​英国排名第一，并成为当时销量最快的首张专辑。该唱片现已在英国获得 BPI 认证的八白金唱片，并在全球售出超过 610 万张。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-top-new-bbc-chart-of-most-streamed-albums-of-nineties-3511041">这是 90 年代英国第二大流媒体专辑</a>，被其继任者《(Wh​​at&#39;s The Story) Morning Glory?》击败，登上榜首。 （1995）。</p><h3> <strong>Oasis 的《Definitely Maybe (30 周年豪华版)》的曲目列表是：</strong></h3><p><strong>第 1 卷</strong><br /><strong>1.《摇滚明星》（重制版）</strong><br /> <strong>2.《Shakermaker》（修复版）</strong><br /> <strong>3.《永远活着》（修复版）</strong><br /> <strong>4.《在天空之上》（修复版）</strong><br /> <strong>5.《哥伦比亚》（重制版）</strong><br /> <strong>6.《超音速》（修复版）</strong><br /> <strong>7.《把它放下》（修复版）</strong><br /> <strong>8.《香烟与酒精》（修复版）</strong><br /> <strong>9.《迪格西的晚餐》（修复版）</strong><br /> <strong>10.《滑走》（修复版）</strong><br /> <strong>11.《结婚生子》（修复版）</strong></p><p><strong>第 2 卷</strong><br /><strong>1.《摇滚明星》（蒙诺谷版）</strong><br /> <strong>2.《Shakermaker》（蒙诺谷版）</strong><br /> <strong>3.《Live Forever》（蒙诺谷版）</strong><br /> <strong>4.《在天空之上》（蒙诺谷版）</strong><br /> <strong>5.《哥伦比亚》（蒙诺谷版）</strong><br /> <strong>6.《Bring It On Down》（蒙诺谷版）</strong><br /> <strong>7.《香烟与酒精》（蒙诺谷版）</strong><br /> <strong>8.《迪格西的晚餐》（蒙诺谷版）</strong><br /> <strong>9.《摇滚明星》（Sawmills Outtake）</strong><br /> <strong>10.《在天空》（Sawmills Outtake）</strong><br /> <strong>11.“哥伦比亚”（锯木厂外）</strong><br /> <strong>12. &#39;Bring It On Down&#39; (Sawmills Outtake)</strong><br /> <strong>13.“香烟和酒精”（锯木厂外卖）</strong><br /> <strong>14.《迪格西的晚餐》（Sawmills Outtake）</strong><br /> <strong>15. &#39;Slide Away&#39; (锯木厂 Outtake)</strong><br /> <strong>16.“悲伤之歌”（莫尔德斯路西演示，92年11月）</strong> </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Noel Gallagher 谈“议会天空”、人工智能绿洲、1975 年和英国脱欧" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/qUl5BVqtNZU?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reunion-or-reissue-fans-are-getting-excited-by-the-new-oasis-teaser-3758069">乐队本周在网上预告了即将重新发行的专辑</a>，让一些歌迷相信他们可能会重聚。去年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/noel-gallagher-confirms-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-reissue-for-2024-denies-oasis-reunion-tour-3436441">诺埃尔确认新版《Definitely Maybe》将于 2024 年推出，</a>以庆祝其三个十年的里程碑。</p><p>与此同时，他关系疏远的兄弟、前乐队成员利亚姆<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-oasis-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-uk-tour-dates-tickets-3515369">将于下个月开始一场特别的“绝对可能”英国和爱尔兰巡演</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-to-play-oasis-definitely-maybe-in-full-at-reading-leeds-2024-3548140#:~:text=Reading%20%26%20Leeds%202024-,Liam%20Gallagher%20to%20play%20Oasis'%20'Definitely%20Maybe'%20in,full%20at%20Reading%20%26%20Leeds%202024&amp;text=Reading%20%26%20Leeds%20have%20confirmed%20that,headline%20the%20festival%20in%202024.">当他在八月的雷丁和利兹音乐节上登上头条时，他还将完整地演奏这张专辑</a>。</p><p> LG此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-says-noel-gallagher-turned-down-definitely-maybe-tour-3516455">声称曾邀请Noel参加他的“Definitely Maybe”节目，但他“拒绝了”</a> 。他开玩笑说<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-promises-naughty-oasis-b-sides-on-definitely-maybe-tour-including-the-noel-sung-half-the-world-away-3513284">他将在演出中演奏一些“顽皮”的 B 面</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-says-he-wont-play-any-solo-material-on-definitely-maybe-tour-3527106">排除了播放他的任何独奏材料</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-says-hes-gonna-go-for-it-visually-on-definitely-maybe-tour-3523756">表示他“会在舞台上以视觉方式呈现”</a> 。</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-release-early-live-version-of-supersonic-for-songs-30th-anniversary-3616860">Oasis 分享了“Supersonic”的早期现场录音，以纪念该乐队首张单曲 30 周年</a>。</p><p>您可以在下方查看 Liam Gallagher 2024 年英国和爱尔兰“Definitely Maybe”巡演日期，并<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/liam-gallagher-tickets/artist/2055477?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=wwEzBLW-RxyPWNIXqSXj8x-BUkHVRdRecSNiXA0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处查找所有剩余门票</a>。</p><h3><strong>利亚姆·加拉格尔将饰演：</strong></h3><p><strong>六月</strong><br /><strong>01 – 谢菲尔德Utilita Arena</strong><br /> <strong>03 – 卡迪夫Utilita Arena</strong><br /> <strong>06 – O2，伦敦</strong><br /><strong>07 – O2，伦敦</strong><br /><strong>10 – O2，伦敦</strong><br /><strong>11 – O2，伦敦</strong><br /><strong>15 – 合作现场，曼彻斯特</strong><br /><strong>16 – 合作现场，曼彻斯特</strong><br /><strong>19 – OVO Hydro，格拉斯哥</strong><br /><strong>20 – OVO Hydro，格拉斯哥</strong><br /><strong>23 – 3Arena, 都柏