.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-Dua-Lipa-new-Camden-docuseries-trailer.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-Dua-Lipa-new-Camden-docuseries-trailer-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-Dua-Lipa-new-Camden-docuseries-trailer-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-Dua-Lipa-new-Camden-docuseries-trailer-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-Dua-Lipa-new-Camden-docuseries-trailer-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/NoelGallagher-Dua-Lipa-new-Camden-docuseries-trailer-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>即将推出的纪录片系列<em>《卡姆登》</em>的官方预告片已分享 - 您可以在下面观看。</p><p>该节目由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)</a>担任执行制作，将与世界上一些最伟大的艺术家一起深入幕后，揭示伦敦卡姆登如何塑造他们的生活和职业生涯的不为人知的故事。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/dua-lipa-radical-optimism-review-lyrics-tracklist-3752802">杜阿·利帕（Dua Lipa）——“激进乐观主义”评论：夏季但轻微的心理流行</a></strong></li></ul><p>该片将于下周三（5 月 29 日）在全球<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/disney">Disney</a> + 和美国 Hulu 首映。</p><p>根据描述，这部由四部分组成的系列将通过<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-martin">克里斯·马丁</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-libertines">浪子乐队</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yungblud">永布鲁德</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">小西姆兹</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nile-rodgers">尼罗·罗杰斯</a>等人的“档案镜头、观察性拍摄和采访”来探索“卡姆登丰富的历史”。</p><p> “聆听世界知名音乐家重温卡姆登经历的声音；从他们的第一场演出到场场爆满的音乐会，夜晚外出的高潮和低谷以及年轻人探索音乐的经历，”它补充道。</p><p>利帕现在分享了<em>《卡姆登》</em>的预告片，由浪荡子乐队的经典歌曲“Don’t Look Back Into The Sun”配乐。</p><p> “卡姆登——充满生机和音乐，”<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">酷玩乐队</a>主唱马丁说道。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">诺埃尔·加拉格尔</a>随后表示，该地区“有心跳”和“氛围”，并补充道：“它充满活力。”</p><p>视频中，利帕一边逛当地的一家唱片店，一边谈论已故的卡姆登偶像<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/amy-winehouse">艾米·怀恩豪斯</a>，随后<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-doherty">皮特·多尔蒂</a>回忆起了过去与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔</a>的冲突。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C7RmZllM7Jq/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,